Use the standard library
This is how to mean_absolute_deviation of numbers:
  Remember that total is 0.000000
  Remember that count is numbers's length
  Remember that index is 0
  Do this count times:
    Remember that total is sum of total and item index in numbers
    Increase index by 1
  End do
  Remember that mean is quotient of total and count
  Remember that deviation_total is 0.000000
  Remember that index is 0
  Do this count times:
    Remember that value is item index in numbers
    When value is less than mean, then:
      Remember that deviation_total is sum of deviation_total and diff of mean and value
    But, if not:
      Remember that deviation_total is sum of deviation_total and diff of value and mean
    End when
    Increase index by 1
  End do
  The answer is quotient of deviation_total and count
Now you know